## Available Agent Skills

Skills are located in:
- Global: `~/.config/zed/skills/<skill-name>/`
- Worktree-specific: `<worktree>/.agents/skills/<skill-name>/`

Each skill contains:
- `SKILL.md` - Main instructions
- `scripts/` - Executable scripts
- `references/` - Additional documentation
- `assets/` - Templates, data files, images

To use a skill, access files directly using bash or file tools:
- Read SKILL.md: `cat ~/.config/zed/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
- Run scripts: `bash ~/.config/zed/skills/<skill-name>/scripts/script.sh`
- Read references: `cat ~/.config/zed/skills/<skill-name>/references/doc.md`

